{"tid":721820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[馬時享惡過雞] 沙中線超支八億攤大手追問政府攞錢","createTime":"2018-06-29T03:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T04:09:05.000Z","uid":74778,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4a45be0c4bbac00e357d8c94b2e553b2d39829a4","tid":721820,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:28:07.000Z","msg":"沙中線超支八億攤大手追問政府攞錢<br />\n恫嚇唔畀錢中方承判商就罰政府利息<br />\n<br />\n在立法會財務委員會上，運輸及房屋局副局長邱誠武指責政府遲遲不肯批出沙中線撥款，怪責議員拖慢批出超支費用，一旦由港鐵墊支費用給其承判工程商如中國建築等，港鐵將向香港政府收取每月高達四百二十萬的利息罰款，長毛直斥邱誠武有無搞錯，運房局監控港鐡不力，未查明地質便批淮工程，事前亦沒有做好地質審查，導致工程一再延誤，政府及港鐵未有先檢討自己錯誤，邱誠武竟還敢指議員拉布引致超支款項未有著落，長毛指出超支無人需要問責，港鐵連續五單工程超支不停伸手問政府拿錢，庫房的錢都平白給了這些中方承建商，貧窮人士分毛得不到，最新公佈的堅尼指數已達0.539 的新高，市民生活艱若，政府卻只懂將金錢拋進無底大白象中。長毛繼而追問財經事務及庫務局常任秘書長謝曼怡，有那一門會計和管理學能讓港鐵這類連連犯錯的公司生存，這一切都是政府政策制定的錯誤，質問為何沙中線超支八億不是港鐵自身管理責任，為何要香港人替港鐵埋單。<br />\n<br />\n#呢個世界公平咩　#七一上街啦<br />\n────────────<br />\n社民連instagram：lsd_hongkong<br />\n捐款支持社民連：<a href=\"http://lsd.org.hk/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flsd.org.hk%2Fdonate&d=McWGvGq8vZ1KCR0AbI8lrW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=88f98711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lsd.org.hk/donate</a><br />\n成為社民連義工：<a href=\"http://www.lsd.org.hk/volunteer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lsd.org.hk%2Fvolunteer&d=McWGvGq8vZ1KCR0AbI8lrW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=718e2413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.lsd.org.hk/volunteer</a><br />\n社民連行動公開資訊：<a href=\"http://telegram.me/lsd_action\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Flsd_action&d=McWGvGq8vZ1KCR0AbI8lrW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=b14e7740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">telegram.me/lsd_action</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/videos/10154544851270785/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhklsd%2Fvideos%2F10154544851270785%2F&d=McWGvGq8vZ1KCR0AbI8lrW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=8b9f14d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/videos/10154544851270785/</a>"},{"pid":"b0c76d83af573ed259126a95b4a1631db5720180","tid":721820,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b247c1c1021d7a84fee1fe8e156b614e95e6ba","tid":721820,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:51:48.000Z","msg":"哩個政府一定比<br />\n跟本唔駛惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38027a335980ac9e2a189d8969d13d2cef3cf997","tid":721820,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"惡過狗"},{"pid":"ee1b6c255d49abb783a5079f045b85179d2f3d27","tid":721820,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:57:38.000Z","msg":"目的同馬來西亞前總理納吉搞果個一馬投資一樣都係明搶國庫錢，一馬投資樣樣失利但因為一馬屬國家企業只有不停泵水落一馬"},{"pid":"218d491d00630e4b872818342cfaefa63823f89e","tid":721820,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:01:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e9f4819089175cd9dbd54cb532a721c75300a4e","tid":721820,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:03:46.000Z","msg":"交下戲畀香港人睇"},{"pid":"80136996c589c54c89622edd3dc35f3b64524bfd","tid":721820,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:09:05.000Z","msg":"炒撚哂批呢個大白象既人"}]}